cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GT, cs.SY, cs.RO

This paper involves deep reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of machine learning and artificial intelligence. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are the most likely categories. The paper also deals with game theory and strategic environments, which suggests that it could belong to cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory). Additionally, the paper involves control theory and decision-making, which could place it in cs.SY (Systems and Control) or cs.RO (Robotics).
